      <h2 class="access-title">Full documentation is available<br><em>under NDA</em> for serious counterparties.</h2>
      <p class="access-body">This page describes the model at a level sufficient to evaluate its credibility and fit. <strong>Full documentation</strong> — including corridor definitions, the complete dependency matrix, simulation API specification, and integration notes — is available on request to qualified counterparties under a standard NDA. Request a demo and we will send the documentation pack before the call.</p>
